This is a functional rewrite of SCP-071, the Degenerative Succubus, originally written on the SCP Editthis Wiki by Anonypoet aka Scroton, and transferred to the SCP Wikidot Wiki by Far2.

I deliberated on approach and considered incorporating the folklore description of succubi as devils that took semen from men and planted it in women, but decided to simply make a direct update of the original post with updated writing standards.

Edit: I removed the unnecessary reference addenda to SCP-112-ARC, as I felt they were no longer relevant.





